sequenceDiagram
  participant User as Usuário
  participant UI as Frontend
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant Embed as Embedding Service
  participant Store as Vector Store
  participant LLM as Gemma 4 via Ollama
  participant DB as SQLite

  User->>UI: Faz pergunta
  UI->>API: POST /api/chat
  API->>Embed: embed(question)
  Embed->>LLM: /api/embed com embeddinggemma
  LLM-->>Embed: query vector
  Embed-->>API: query vector
  API->>Store: search(vector, top_k)
  Store->>DB: consulta vetorial/similaridade
  DB-->>Store: chunks candidatos
  Store-->>API: chunks + scores
  API->>LLM: prompt com contexto + pergunta
  LLM-->>API: resposta
  API->>DB: salva mensagens e trace
  API-->>UI: answer + sources + trace_id
  UI-->>User: exibe resposta e fontes
